      "text": [
        " رِوَايَةِ اَلسَّكُونِيِّ قَالَ كَانَ عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَقُولُ: \"اِنْهَوْا نِسَاءَكُمْ أَنْ يُرْضِعْنَ يَمِيناً وَ شِمَالاً فَإِنَّهُنَّ يَنْسَيْنَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4676 - In the narration of Al-Sakooni, it is reported that Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) used to say, \"Prevent your women from breastfeeding here and there (to various children), for they may forget.\""
        ]
      }
    },
